lead_paragraph: Gilles Simon rallied to beat Julien Benneteau 4-6, 6-3, 6-2 in an all-French match in the first round of the Paris Masters on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Simon Rallies to Beat Benneteau in Paris Masters First Round
